lyrics:
15 contributorsoverslept lyricsverse 1 faye webster
i always oversleep
im always next to you
do you see me in your dreams
cause i see you see me too
at times my mind feels too full
and i want to empty it
but im scared to write my thoughts down
in case someone steals them

chorus faye webster
but i got you
i got you
i got you
i got you

verse 2 mei ehara
ばらけた朝は夜を抱えて
虫食う心のそばに花を植え
蛇口を落ちる水の音から
何もかもが見えてしまって

あなた　隣で
溢れて　見つけてよsee faye webster liveget tickets as low as 49you might also likeembed
